<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idfe8a0e2b-9d45-11f0-a0db-bff75580f504" identifier="/us/usc/t24/s15"><num value="15">§ 15.</num><heading> Superintendence of Navy hospitals</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Navy shall have the general charge and superintendence of Navy hospitals.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idfe8a0e2c-9d45-11f0-a0db-bff75580f504">(R.S. § 4807.)</sourceCredit>
